  <name>ZenDownload</name>
  <summary>Fast, modern download manager</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      ZenDownload is a fast, modern download manager that aims to be the best
      alternative to IDM and JDownloader. It supports HTTP, HTTPS, FTP, torrents,
      video extraction from 1000+ sites, HLS/DASH streams, batch downloading,
      link checking, format conversion, and site crawling.
    </p>
    <p>Key features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Multi-threaded accelerated downloads (up to 64 connections)</li>
      <li>Torrent engine with full session restore</li>
      <li>Video stream extraction via yt-dlp (YouTube, Twitter, TikTok, etc.)</li>
      <li>Live TV streaming with 11,000+ IPTV channels</li>
      <li>Batch URL import with category assignment</li>
      <li>Built-in link checker (HTTP HEAD, file size, type detection)</li>
      <li>Format converter (FFmpeg-based, 9 built-in presets)</li>
      <li>Site crawler/grabber (BFS, file-type filtering, depth control)</li>
      <li>System tray with pause/resume all, downloads folder quick access</li>
      <li>Browser extension for Chrome/Edge/Firefox (manifest V3)</li>
      <li>CLI and REST API for automation</li>
      <li>Cross-platform: Windows, macOS, Linux (.deb, AppImage, Flatpak)</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
